sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant U as User Browser
  participant A as ASP.NET Core API
  participant D as PostgreSQL 17 (RLS)

  U->>A: POST /api/auth/login (email/password)
  A->>A: Verify PBKDF2 password hash (PasswordHasher)
  A->>A: Issue HS256 JWT (sub, email, name)
  A-->>U: { accessToken, user }
  U->>A: API request with Bearer JWT
  A->>A: Validate issuer/audience/signature/expiry
  A->>D: BEGIN
  A->>D: SET LOCAL role authenticated
  A->>D: select set_config('app.user_id', user_id, true)
  A->>D: Execute tenant query
  D->>D: RLS checks organization_members
  D-->>A: Authorized rows only
  A->>D: COMMIT
  A-->>U: Response
